{"id": "1220050076114882570", "channel_id": "1220050076114882570", "type": 0, "author_id": "968857106985910302", "author_name": "enosred", "author_bot": false, "content": "时灵摆潜游和群星之酒+单独触发的时候都可以正常触发增加狂气效果，但是当同时触发时通过录屏慢速拖视频进度条就可以发现伤害是跳了4下但是增加狂气效果只跳了3下。（其中+2是白银造物银色方扣缎带的效果）\n就正常的触发逻辑应该是：下张满级打击a造物生效2次+b造物生效2次。2+2那结果应该是4次伤害+40狂气对吧？但从视频里可以看出来只给我加了30…\n过几天活动的共鸣就点满了造物上限到时候有16个！这种时灵摆和黄金造物+的交互还会更多的！快修！！！", "timestamp": "2024-03-20T16:43:25.580000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1220050077192687676", "filename": "RPReplay_Final1710951523.mov", "content_type": "video/quicktime", "size": 4669018, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1220050076114882570/1220050077192687676/RPReplay_Final1710951523.mov?ex=6a00b5ad&is=69ff642d&hm=9f93ed881131ed5a90ba67d04b3a650a5c660458a257854d3bbc4caf6be73fd8&"}, {"id": "1220050077821829300", "filename": "RPReplay_Final1710951560.mov", "content_type": "video/quicktime", "size": 5200620, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1220050076114882570/1220050077821829300/RPReplay_Final1710951560.mov?ex=6a00b5ad&is=69ff642d&hm=e8e51a6dc79a52db7a0e4e818d69080b2e22d86c21d512b78c91239d9aa16a0f&"}, {"id": "1220050078430138528", "filename": "RPReplay_Final1710951620.mov", "content_type": "video/quicktime", "size": 10213261, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1220050076114882570/1220050078430138528/RPReplay_Final1710951620.mov?ex=6a00b5ae&is=69ff642e&hm=b0c8c8222133bf8baf945859cd558eab900ec9b6c80f30806ca10252223b9b92&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1220050076114882570", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」关于当时灵摆潜游和群星之酒+同时触发的情况下的吞狂气问题", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
{"id": "1220063009167114372", "channel_id": "1220063009167114372", "type": 0, "author_id": "733514425847513171", "author_name": "xuan4185", "author_bot": false, "content": "很明顯，小小心願的“置入”手牌並變成0費的效果被詭術禮帽的“抽牌”時生效的效果判定為抽牌，故詭術禮帽再次替小小心願的費用做1~3的浮動，但“置入”不應該等價於“抽入”。\n\n然而我上述說的很有可能都是錯的。\n\n在我第二個影片中，可以看到吞噬後回手的小小心願，實際算力消耗是從3＞2，且第一支影片是2＞1，倒是可以推測小小心願實際的效果是將牌費-1再置入手牌中。\n\n但也有可能只是巧合。", "timestamp": "2024-03-20T17:34:49.060000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-03-21T00:38:39.859000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [{"id": "1220063009729417277", "filename": "Screen_Recording_20240321_010136.mp4", "content_type": "video/mp4", "size": 4914388, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1220063009167114372/1220063009729417277/Screen_Recording_20240321_010136.mp4?ex=6a00c1b9&is=69ff7039&hm=7dfb092668276659f97498b0853f69c19d7b60eb71b4303e3f5823e2e6aa1721&"}, {"id": "1220063010350170352", "filename": "Screenshot_20240321_012124.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 190232, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1220063009167114372/1220063010350170352/Screenshot_20240321_012124.jpg?ex=6a00c1b9&is=69ff7039&hm=2f4132170b2f8064cff833d60340bed40c00a26b087a9132be1cf832b32ce94b&"}, {"id": "1220063010765148240", "filename": "Screenshot_20240321_012133.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 203522, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1220063009167114372/1220063010765148240/Screenshot_20240321_012133.jpg?ex=6a00c1b9&is=69ff7039&hm=acf513bdb7b82d3929ac14ec7345932e1998dc2b249b38e9274ec3b820c45a8e&"}, {"id": "1220063011025191002", "filename": "Screen_Recording_20240321_012854.mp4", "content_type": "video/mp4", "size": 4110653, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1220063009167114372/1220063011025191002/Screen_Recording_20240321_012854.mp4?ex=6a00c1b9&is=69ff7039&hm=77bf392389b4870006d7530862f8ed600311fa37bb7b44451602083d221f2c5e&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread