{"id": "1219848135635894283", "channel_id": "1219848135635894283", "type": 0, "author_id": "757961390412660836", "author_name": "crimsonkiss", "author_bot": false, "content": "我超喜欢这游戏在游戏页面右下角放当地时间。但我不理解为何至今还是不放自回体力所需时间…\n强烈建议给自回体力放个所需时间，另外也希望可以有个widget，上面也会显示自回体力状况。\n感恩！", "timestamp": "2024-03-20T03:20:59.218000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 5}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1219848135635894283", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」时间…", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1219932429469487164", "channel_id": "1219932429469487164", "type": 0, "author_id": "392840163732226058", "author_name": "vegoutdino", "author_bot": false, "content": "作用於傷害：傷害先向上取一次整數後，進行傷害強效計算，最後再向上取一次整數。\n作用於中毒/反擊：以取整前的小數進行傷害強效計算，最後向上取一次整數。\n\n舉莉莉的5等打擊與5等黑沼為例：\n兩者分別為18%攻擊力的傷害/中毒，\n對應60等莉莉104攻擊力，則背後的數值為18.72進位成19\n\n進入關卡後，隊伍以12%的傷害強效影響，\n莉莉打擊變成19 * 112% = 22 (21.28)\n但黑沼中毒卻是18.72 * 112% = 21 (20.97)\n想詢問在這兩處應用上的不同是有意如此設計的嗎@@?", "timestamp": "2024-03-20T08:55:56.434000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-03-20T08:56:43.041000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 7}], "attachments": [{"id": "1219932625502863471", "filename": "ABECAEB7-A90B-4E98-B327-E0BD7882288E.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1899087, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1219932429469487164/1219932625502863471/ABECAEB7-A90B-4E98-B327-E0BD7882288E.png?ex=6a00484b&is=69fef6cb&hm=08de23cb674942cc40e283e31b6540cfcd1447fbcff96e43d3fa7c92077d9c88&"}, {"id": "1219932626136334336", "filename": "F757C10E-FB13-4562-AD93-18ACB1649F8D.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 945538, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1219932429469487164/1219932626136334336/F757C10E-FB13-4562-AD93-18ACB1649F8D.png?ex=6a00484b&is=69fef6cb&hm=5d39a51fc7a1e45c4d743892a316e494b3bde7294829e59e9b047f259ab7b965&"}, {"id": "1219932626685526026", "filename": "81C993BE-C30C-4066-B2B4-D305B69E040A.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 753607, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1219932429469487164/1219932626685526026/81C993BE-C30C-4066-B2B4-D305B69E040A.png?ex=6a00484b&is=69fef6cb&hm=1b8454c30cecd5d796ad0f2d0ace350d7f7fe1931ad59a66641e9294846d049f&"}, {"id": "1219932627369459732", "filename": "B8EA56DA-3258-4E5A-AAD1-ECC8A5691056.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1668119, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1219932429469487164/1219932627369459732/B8EA56DA-3258-4E5A-AAD1-ECC8A5691056.png?ex=6a00484b&is=69fef6cb&hm=8ab9a703963d3c51f5d3bd207c64896eac8ab2036e41758436a8fef84f8d9090&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1219932429469487164", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "💭「處理中」傷害強效作用於傷害與中毒反擊的方式不一樣", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
